com.anaplan.client

Class ServerFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.anaplan.client.AnaplanApiClientObject
      • com.anaplan.client.NamedObject
        • com.anaplan.client.ServerFile

  • public class ServerFile
extends NamedObject
    Represents a file on the Anaplan server associated with a model.

    For importing data a file is first uploaded then its associated import is run. When exporting data an export process is run, then the resulting server file is downloaded

      • getUploadStream

        public OutputStream getUploadStream()
                             throws AnaplanAPIException,
                                    IOException
        Return a new OutputStream implementation which will upload written content to the server, writing it to the specified target file. Any existing data will be replaced. The server file will be considered incomplete until the close() method is invoked on the OutputStream
        Returns:
        The OutputStream to write to
        Throws:
        AnaplanAPIException
        IOException
        Since:
        1.2

      • getUploadCellWriter

        @Deprecated
public CellWriter getUploadCellWriter()
                               throws AnaplanAPIException
        Deprecated. 
        Return a CellWriter implementation which will upload written content to the server, writing it to the specified target file. The file will have the following format:
        • Encoding: UTF-8
        • Column separator: tab character
        • Delimiter: none - the presence of a tab character in a cell will cause an exception to be thrown
        • Header row number: 1
        • First data row: 2
        Returns:
        a CellWriter implementation
        Throws:
        AnaplanAPIException
        Since:
        1.2
